com.communote.server.core.vo.query

Class TaggingCoreItemUTPExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.vo.query.TaggingCoreItemUTPExtension

  • public class TaggingCoreItemUTPExtension
extends Object
    Extension for the CoreItemQueryInstance which holds Note specific data. Note: Instances of this class can't be used for multiple users without setting a new user id, as the user id is per default set to the id of the first user, who created an instances of this class.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
